  "title": "ELECTRIC CABLE JOINTER",
  "description": "<p>· Carry out cable spiking.</p>\n<p>· Carry out cable termination.</p>\n<p>· Connect generator power and cables in accordance to code of practice.</p>\n<p>· Fix cables that are not working, while following safety rules.</p>\n<p>· Install low and high voltage, and cable joints in accordance to project blueprints.</p>\n<p>· Maintain safety in the work area.</p>\n<p>· Perform cable inspection.</p>\n<p>· Perform cable jointing in accordance to standard code of practice.</p>\n<p>· Trace High Voltage cable joint failure.</p>\n<p>· work indoors, outdoors and in confined spaces.</p>\n<p>· have to stand for long hours, climb, bend and kneel for cable works.</p>\n<p>· expected to be detail oriented to ensure safety on job.</p>",
